CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence and woman wearing West African attire looking at large book on podium with eagle shaped base, with men in background, in Office of the Mayor, City County Building
